State of Connecticut v. Brian E. Kicklighter (9128)

O’Connell, Foti and Landau, Js.

Argued January 17 decision released February 5, 1991 *808Nicholas P. Cardwell, for the appellant (defendant). Leah Hawley, assistant state’s attorney, with whom, on the brief, were Donald Caldwell, state’s attorney, and Sandra Tullis, deputy assistant state’s attorney, for the appellee (state). Per Curiam.

The judgment is affirmed.
